edu.usc.pgroup.goffish.gofs

Interface ISubgraphTemplate

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IGraph<TemplateVertex,TemplateEdge>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TemplateGraph

    public interface ISubgraphTemplate
extends IGraph<TemplateVertex,TemplateEdge>
    This interface represents a subgraph template, which contains the structure of the subgraph, i.e. the vertices and edges.
